divs: sighting detailsthe wife and i were on santa rosa island around june 8th 2010. took some pictures and video of the beach stayed 1\2 hour or so, went home. i'm just now looking at eh photos in further detail and i see things in the sky the sunlight glinting off the body of a huge craft... there are several objects in these 2 pictures .... i see all sorts of what could be spacecraft.... i know it sounds crazy but maybe the angle of the sunset and camera saw the craft... cuz supposedly these ships ive heard about that use clouds to hide their prescence.... take a look and tell me what u think?
